This version of Pines is incomplete and many changes are coming, possibly even
major structural changes. This file is a feature plan.

Read the INSTALL file for installation instructions.

Planned features for versions <=1.0:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
+Installer/Package Manager.
+Use entity references in com_user.
+Fix and improve com_newsletter.
+Full SAWASC A implementation for better security.
	(http://sawasc.sciactive.com/)
+More log entries.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Planned features for versions >1.0:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
+Entity locking.
+Pines Grid caption and summary support.
+New templates / Improve Pines template. (Maybe use XSL instead of PHP.)
+An entity exporter/importer. Also a backup creator. Use the metadata of a PJA
	to hold the entity export. It would provide a full backup.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------